{"tid":2321720,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底呢個年代ol有無需要畀家用？","createTime":"2020-12-11T17:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T20:24:01.000Z","uid":14304,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7dac0eda5e629c3c30b8461cc1ca56055da3b0","tid":2321720,"uid":14304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"我家就有兩兄弟，我係細佬。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就每個月都有畀家用，但阿哥呢，就覺得完全<br />\n<br />\n無需要畀，而家佢負責畀緊兩個月交一次嘅雜費，<br />\n<br />\n都係屋企人同佢傾咗勁耐先肯畀。<br />\n<br />\n佢仲打算搬出去住，佢就認為搬埋出去就連而家屋<br />\n<br />\n企雜費都唔洗負責。<br />\n<br />\n所以我真係諗咗好耐到底點先可以勸到佢要畀家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 需要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔需要"},{"pid":"9955c2a9db0477574bc1328f0bcca1a66a9cbdbb","tid":2321720,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"你係咪搵得多過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7dbf8f17fc8d1f70efc1454e1d3a4a7199a1ce","tid":2321720,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"咩係ol"},{"pid":"66f4a548f83af39d3619ff55ee1e919de8b1d154","tid":2321720,"uid":211878,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"兩兄弟邊到走個OL出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"52538df02ed5db49b6b6fedc2832263185254228","tid":2321720,"uid":211878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66f4a548f83af39d3619ff55ee1e919de8b1d154","tid":2321720,"uid":211878,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"兩兄弟邊到走個OL出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl